'''翠雀花素'''（英文：delphinidin) ，也叫'''飞燕草素'''、'''花翠素'''，是最常见的[[花青素|花青素]]之一，既是一种[[生物色素|植物色素]]也是一种[[抗氧化剂|抗氧化剂]]。<ref>{{cite journal | title = Delphinidin, an anthocyanidin in pigmented fruits and vegetables, protects human HaCaT keratinocytes and mouse skin against UVB-mediated oxidative stress and apoptosis | author = AFAQ Farrukh; SYED Deeba N.; MALIK Arshi; HADI Naghma; SARFARAZ Sami; KWEON Mee-Hyang; KHAN Naghma; MOHAMMAD ABU ZAID; MUKHTAR Hasan | journal = Journal of investigative dermatology | year = 2007 | volume = 127 | issue = 1 | pages = 222–232 | doi = 10.1038/sj.jid.5700510}}</ref> 翠雀花素在[[翠雀属|翠雀属]]和[[堇菜属|堇菜属]]植物中的存在导致显现蓝色。<ref name="Eno">{{Cite journal | author = Ribereau-Gayon, Jean; Ribereau-Gayon, Pascal | title = The anthocyans and leucoanthocyans of grapes and wines | journal = American Journal of Enology  | year = 1958 | volume = 9 | pages = 1–9}}</ref>它还给了[[赤霞珠|赤霞珠]][[葡萄|葡萄]]的蓝红色，并且存在于[[越橘属|越橘属]][[浆果|浆果]]、康科德葡萄和[[石榴|石榴]]中。<ref name="Eno" />像几乎所有其他花色素一样，翠雀花素是[[pH值|pH值]]敏感的，并且在酸性[[溶液|溶液]]中变为红色，在碱性溶液中变为蓝色。

翠雀花素是一种很好的[[酸碱指示剂|酸碱指示剂]]，遇碱变蓝，遇酸变红。

== [[糖苷|糖苷]]衍生物 ==
由翠雀花素衍生的[[花色素苷|花色素苷]]包括蓝翠雀花苷（cyanodelphin）、紫翠雀花苷（violdelphin）、郁金香花苷（tulipanin）、{{le|黑果越橘苷|myrtillin}}（myrtillin）、茄色苷（nasunin）等。

蓝翠雀花苷、{{le|紫翠雀花苷|violdelphin}}和{{le|郁金香花苷|tulipanin}}分别负责[[翠雀花|翠雀花]]的蓝色、紫色和粉紫色。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Analysis of the flower pigments of some ''Delphinium'' species and their interspecific hybrids produced via ovule culture|author=Kazushige, Honda; Kiyoshi Tsutsuia; Keizo, Hosokawa|url=https://doi.org/10.1016/S0304-4238(99)00039-4|journal=Scientia Horticulturae|issue=|doi=|others=|year=1999|volume=82|page=125-134|pmid=}}</ref>

